projects.name: Parkinson's Disease Detection using Speech Dataset
projects.description: Collaborated with healthcare professionals on a project focused on detecting Parkinson's disease using machine learning algorithms applied to speech data. Analyzed and processed a diverse dataset to train models, achieving an impressive accuracy rate of 85%. The project aimed to facilitate early diagnosis and management of Parkinson's disease through efficient and accurate detection methods. Tech Stack used Python, Scikit-learn, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Flask
